    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="1206863731">
        <div class="comment">
            <h3>
                <span class="comment-vote">
                    <span id="c-1206863731" class="vote-count">0</span>
                        <a href="javascript:;" id="btn-1206863731" class="j a_show_login" data-cid="1206863731">有用</a>
                </span>
                <span class="comment-info">
                    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/94829797/">不想拾人牙慧</a>
                        <span class="user-stars allstar50 rating" title="力荐"></span>
                    <span>2017-06-24</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">人如果胖了，可能希望镜子里的自己显得瘦；人如果瘦，可能希望镜子中的自己显得壮实。但哈哈镜中的自己还是自己吗？《金瓶梅》就是一面真实的镜子，人性全在里面了</p>
        </div>
    </li>

                
    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="1206423702">
        <div class="comment">
            <h3>
                <span class="comment-vote">
                    <span id="c-1206423702" class="vote-count">0</span>
                        <a href="javascript:;" id="btn-1206423702" class="j a_show_login" data-cid="1206423702">有用</a>
                </span>
                <span class="comment-info">
                    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/Schicksalslied/">打铁</a>
                        <span class="user-stars allstar50 rating" title="力荐"></span>
                    <span>2017-06-23</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">写李瓶儿死前一段，真是何等手笔：病状污秽，不堪之甚；求医，而只得庸医；求医不成求神，又获罪于天；命终之际种种安排，各路人真真假假。只此一节，觉西门庆多少有些真情在。</p>
        </div>
    </li>

                
    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="1205972912">
        <div class="comment">
            <h3>
                <span class="comment-vote">
